data.description: Welcome home to 200 Baugher Drive. This warm ranch-style home located in the heart of Hanover boasts over 2,200 sqft. This home offers a comfortable living space with an open kitchen plan and dining area create a great place to dine and entertain. Inside, you'll find full baths with stylish tile showers, adding a touch of modern comfort. The owners suite is separated from the three aux. bedrooms and offers a spacious haven, with cathedral ceilings and filled with natural light. Venture downstairs to the lower level, where a cozy fireplace adds a touch of charm and warmth, perfect additional separate living space. Step outside to the backyard, where a welcoming covered patio area with cathedral cedar ceilings provides an excellent space for outdoor living, whether you're enjoying your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue. Schedule your showing today and make this delightful property your own!
